org.apache.livy

Interface JobHandle<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Future<T>

    public interface JobHandle<T>
extends Future<T>
    A handle to a submitted job. Allows for monitoring and controlling of the running remote job.

    • Nested Class Summary

        void addListener(JobHandle.Listener<T> l)
